        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"734814\">Dexin Zhang</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Does.20match.20imply.20equality.3F/near/463724548\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>You can try this:</p>\n<p><div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">chainMatch</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Node</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">chain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is_of_chain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">false</span>\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Thanks, it worked. I've been staring at this problem for a while, didn't even think you could do that</p>",
